      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties sourced from lot-specific coupon tests; geometric inputs from calibrated CMM measurements of test articles; input uncertainty quantified.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114.2 GPa) and yield strength (896 MPa) derived from Ti-6Al-4V ELI coupon data (dataVintage 2025-08-01). Geometry from CMM measurements of three production screws (mean ± 1 SD reported). Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (N=1000); combined input uncertainty contribution to stiffness QoI = ±2.3%. The September 2025 model revision updated thread-root fillet radius by 0.05 mm and adjusted contact stiffness scaling factor from 1.0 to 0.95; the assessment team determined these changes did not materially affect the material property inputs or require re-characterisation of the Ti-6Al-4V lot."
    },
